@node WIN_TSLC "JV-1080/Tone Select/Edit"

This window determines which Tone you will see in the windows and which Tones will
be affected by changes made by you.

The currently selected Tone which you see in the windows is always edited.

By using the "All/None" function you can quickly edit all the Tones or just the
selected one.

@endnode

@node WIN "JV-1080/Windows"

Click on a button to get info on that particular window. All the
windows have context sensitive help so you can just press the
<HELP> button to get help on the currently active window.

@{" Main Window " link WIN_MAIN}
@{" Patch Bank Window " link WIN_PBNK}
@{" Patch Common Window" link PCMN}
@{" Patch Effects Window" link PEFX}
@{" Settings Window " link PREF}

@endnode

